    "Recently, AI techniques have been widely used to solve the complicated resource allocation problems in a data-driven manner, bypassing the accurate system modeling and mathematical derivations.",
    "Compared with the traditional non-convex optimization algorithms, AI techniques are more suitable for online deployment and time-varying environment.",
    "The AI-based resource allocation for ISAC is shown in Figure 15, where the AI techniques are used to allocate the multi-domain resource to strike a good balance between the two functionalities.Wang et al. [230] investigated subcarrier and power allocation for OFDM-based ISAC networks under the time-varying environment.",
    "The power consumption was minimized while satisfying the requirements of both communication and sensing.",
    "They developed an online optimization framework based on DRL to handle this non-convex stochastic optimization problem."
